    {
      "name": "WebSocket – Info",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "⚠ WebSocket STOMP (hors Postman)",
          "id": "6baa14b5-b506-423e-84bc-2a5efc7c44f7",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{notif_base}}/ws/info",
              "host": [
                "{{notif_base}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "ws",
                "info"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ce GET vérifie que l'endpoint SockJS répond (retourne un JSON de négociation SockJS).\n\nPour recevoir des notifications en temps réel, utiliser Hoppscotch (hoppscotch.io → Realtime → STOMP) :\n- URL    : ws://localhost:8089/ws/websocket\n- Subscribe : /topic/notifications/{spectateurId}\n\nFormat du message reçu :\n{\n  \"id\": 42,\n  \"type\": \"INCIDENT\",\n  \"contenu\": \"Nouvel incident (TECHNIQUE) à Tribune A: Incident test\",\n  \"dateEnvoi\": \"2026-02-27T10:00:00\",\n  \"idEvent\": 1001,\n  \"idSpectateur\": 1,\n  \"sourceEventId\": \"evt-abc-123\",\n  \"lu\": false\n}"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "id": "11676ff9-338c-47fb-b1de-46e8213c8a85"
    }
